snippet.title: WWE 2K Battlegrounds Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the teaser trailer for WWE 2K Battlegrounds and Brawl Without Limits, coming September 18, 2020.

Pre-order now: https://wwe.2k.com/battlegrounds/buy

Visit the official website at https://wwe.2k.com/battlegrounds for more news.
